程序包 org.janusgraph.diskstorage.hbase

接口 AdminMask

所有超级接口:
AutoCloseable, Closeable
所有已知实现类:
HBaseAdmin1_0
public interface AdminMask
extends Closeable
This interface hides ABI/API breaking changes that HBase has made to its Admin/HBaseAdmin over the course of development from 0.94 to 1.0 and beyond.

    • getEstimatedRegionServerCount

      int getEstimatedRegionServerCount()
      Estimate the number of regionservers in the HBase cluster. This is usually implemented by calling Admin.getClusterStatus() and then ClusterStatus.getServers() and finally size() on the returned server list.
      返回:
      the number of servers in the cluster or -1 if it could not be determined
